Tod’s Della Valle Targets RCS Stake of as Much as 20%, Sole Says

-- B y   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t
-- 
2011-06-11T10:24:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-11/tod-s-della-valle-targets-rcs-stake-of-as-much-as-20-sole-says.html
Diego Della Valle, chief executive
officer of  Tod’s SpA (TOD) , aims to increase its stake in  RCS
MediaGroup SpA (RCS)  to as much as 20 percent,  Il Sole 24 Ore  said,
without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tommaso Ebhardt in Milan at 
 tebhardt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chad Thomas at   cthomas16@bloomberg.net . 